Class AssetInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zonarsystems.twenty20.sdk.deviceprofile.AssetInfo
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class AssetInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is deprecated as of March 22, 2017. Use SafeAssetInfo instead. The type Asset info contains all the data associated with a Zonar Asset. De-serialized from JSON -- Beware of removing "unused" fields and methods.
